''' 2015年哥本哈根连环枪击案'''是於[[欧洲中部时间|欧洲中部时间]]2015年2月14日16:00在[[丹麦|丹麦]][[哥本哈根|哥本哈根]]名为“艺术、亵渎和言论自由”的纪念1月份[[查理周刊总部枪击案|查理周刊总部枪击案]]受害者的公众活动中发生的一宗[[枪击案|枪击案]]。最值得注意的是，被认为是枪击案的主要目标的艺术家拉尔斯·威尔克斯（Lars Vilks）参与了本次会议。其他出席人员包括[[丹麦人民党|丹麦人民党]]议会成员杰特·普尔斯纳·达利（Jette Plesner Dali）和法国驻丹麦大使弗朗索瓦·泽米雷（Francois Zimeray）。事件中共有1名平民死亡，另外有3名警察受伤<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/02/14/us-denmark-shooting-idUSKBN0LI0N720150214|title=Man dies in shooting at Danish meeting with artist who drew Mohammad|work=Reuters}}</ref>。

枪击案数小时后，位于市区水晶街（Krystalgade）附近的犹太教堂发生第二起枪击案，造成1名平民死亡，两名警察受伤。目前尚未证实是否与枪击案有关<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.yahoo.com/shots-fired-copenhagen-synagogue-danish-police-002559779.html|title=Shots fired at Copenhagen synagogue: Danish police|date=14 February 2015|work=[[Yahoo!_News|Yahoo! News]]|accessdate=14 February 2015|archive-date=2015-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150220034745/http://news.yahoo.com/shots-fired-copenhagen-synagogue-danish-police-002559779.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 炸药桶咖啡店枪击案 ==
[[File:The_Press_@_Krudttønden_-cphshootings_(16350275819).jpg|thumb]]
致力于支持瑞典艺术家[[拉尔斯·威尔克斯|拉尔斯·威尔克斯]]言论自由权的丹麦组织拉尔斯·威尔克斯委员会，宣布了名为“艺术、亵渎和言论自由”（{{lang-da|Kunst, blasfemi og ytringsfrihed}}）的公共研讨会<ref>{{cite web|url=http://larsvilks.com/2015/01/24/kom-til-debatmode-14-februar/|title=Kom til debatmøde 14. februar|work=Lars Vilks|access-date=2015-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150412064248/http://larsvilks.com/2015/01/24/kom-til-debatmode-14-februar/|archive-date=2015-04-12|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。活动2015年2月14日欧洲中部时间15:00于丹麦哥本哈根的Østerbro区Østerfælled Torv街的Krudttønden文化中心举办<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.krudttonden.dk/26085.1131.8/Fatwa%20eller%20ytringsfrihed|title=Krudttønden|work=krudttonden.dk|access-date=2015-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150216032605/http://www.krudttonden.dk/26085.1131.8/Fatwa%20eller%20ytringsfrihed|archive-date=2015-02-16|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。会议原定讨论1月份针对法国讽刺周刊《[[查理周刊|查理周刊]]》的[[查理周刊总部枪击案|袭击案]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://minby.dk/oesterbro-avis/debatmoede-om-charlie-hebdo/|title=Debatmøde om Charlie Hebdo|work=Østerbro Avis|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150423042637/http://minby.dk/oesterbro-avis/debatmoede-om-charlie-hebdo/|archivedate=2015-04-23|accessdate=2015-02-16}}</ref>。

15:33，一名55岁的出席活动男子被打死。3名警察被流弹打伤<ref>{{cite news |title=One dead and three injured in Copenhagen 'terrorist attack' |author=Chris Johnston |url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/feb/14/copenhagen-blasphemy-lars-vilks-prophet-muhammad-krudttonden-cafe |newspaper=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] |date=14 February 2015 |accessdate=15 February 2015 |archive-date=2015-02-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150215012456/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/feb/14/copenhagen-blasphemy-lars-vilks-prophet-muhammad-krudttonden-cafe |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="dr113410" />，其中两名是隶属于丹麦安全和情报局的保镖。警察们返回现场驳火，迫使袭击者逃离现场<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/world/one-dead-three-police/1659726.html|title=One dead, three police hurt in shooting at Copenhagen Islam debate|newspaper=Channel News Asia|quote="fled the scene after a shootout with police"|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150423063013/http://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/world/one-dead-three-police/1659726.html|archivedate=2015-04-23|accessdate=2015-02-16}}</ref>。现场的窗户至少留下30个弹孔，可以从知名的爵士音乐会场所看到<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.msnbc.com/msnbc/new-shooting-copenhagen-after-attack-freedom-event-cafe|title=New shooting in Copenhagen after attack on freedom event at cafe|work=MSNBC|accessdate=15 February 2015|archive-date=2015-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150215034016/http://www.msnbc.com/msnbc/new-shooting-copenhagen-after-attack-freedom-event-cafe|dead-url=no}}</ref>。法国驻丹麦大使弗朗索瓦·泽米雷参加了本次会议<ref name=hp>{{cite web|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.fr/2015/02/14/danemark-fusillade-copenhague-debat-islamisme-liberte-expressio_n_6683918.html?|title=Danemark: une fusillade éclate à Copenhague à l'extérieur d'un bâtiment où se tenait un débat sur l'islamisme et la liberté d'expression|work=Le Huffington Post|language=fr|accessdate=2015-02-16|archive-date=2015-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150321110519/http://www.huffingtonpost.fr/2015/02/14/danemark-fusillade-copenhague-debat-islamisme-liberte-expressio_n_6683918.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，他表示：“直觉上我认为至少有50声枪响，但这里的警方说有200枪<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://news.yahoo.com/one-dead-copenhagen-shooting-171538319.html|title = Two dead, five injured in Copenhagen shootings|last = Billing|first = Sören|date = 15 February 2015|work = Yahoo! News|access-date = 15 February 2015|archive-date = 2015-02-16|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150216085729/http://news.yahoo.com/one-dead-copenhagen-shooting-171538319.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>。”

其他出席活动的人士还有[[FEMEN|FEMEN]]女权活动家[[伊娜·舍甫琴科|伊娜·舍甫琴科]]<ref name=hp/>、在会上发言<ref>{{cite news|title=Twin attacks in Copenhagen leave one dead, six injured|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/denmark/11413520/Twin-attacks-in-Copenhagen-leave-one-dead-six-injured.html|accessdate=15 February 2014|work=The Telegraph|date=14 February 2014|archive-date=2015-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150216000457/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/denmark/11413520/Twin-attacks-in-Copenhagen-leave-one-dead-six-injured.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>的《Dagbladet Information》编辑尼尔斯·伊瓦尔·拉森<ref>{{cite news|last1=Ruud|first1=Hans-Martin Thomt|title=Halvtime etter attentatforsøket twitret den franske ambassadøren: - Fortsatt i live|url=http://www.dagbladet.no/2015/02/14/nyheter/utenriks/attentatforsok/37717294/|accessdate=15 February 2015|work=Dagbladet Nyheter|date=14 February 2015|archive-date=2015-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150214224338/http://www.dagbladet.no/2015/02/14/nyheter/utenriks/attentatforsok/37717294/|dead-url=no}}</ref>和组织者赫勒·莫雷特·百利，百利表示袭击针对的目标是威尔克斯<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/europe/reports-shots-fired-at-copenhagen-cafe-free-speech-event/2015/02/14/e34f4d5c-b460-11e4-bf39-5560f3918d4b_story.html|title=Shootout at Copenhagen cafe free speech event|publisher=Washington Post|date=14 February 2015|author=Associated Press|accessdate=2015-02-16|archive-date=2015-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150214185258/http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/europe/reports-shots-fired-at-copenhagen-cafe-free-speech-event/2015/02/14/e34f4d5c-b460-11e4-bf39-5560f3918d4b_story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

案发后，犯罪嫌疑人乘坐一辆胁持过来的深色[[大众波罗|大众波罗]]逃离现场，警方警告潜在的目击者直接碰到他们时，不要接近车辆<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nbcnews.com/news/world/shots-fired-copenhagen-cafe-free-speech-event-hosted-lars-vilks-n306316|title=Shots Fired at Copenhagen Cafe Free Speech Event Hosted by Lars Vilks|publisher=NBC News|date=14 February 2015|accessdate=2015-02-16|archive-date=2015-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151118134516/http://www.nbcnews.com/news/world/shots-fired-copenhagen-cafe-free-speech-event-hosted-lars-vilks-n306316|dead-url=no}}</ref>。这辆车后来被发现荒废在几公里之外的地方<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dr.dk/Nyheder/Indland/2015/02/14/175113.htm|title=Flugtbil efter attentatforsøg er fundet|first=Mette|last=Stender Pedersen|work=DR.dk|date=14 February 2015|accessdate=14 February 2015|trans_title=Getaway car after assassination attempt found|language=da|archive-date=2015-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150214190153/https://www.dr.dk/Nyheder/Indland/2015/02/14/175113.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

丹麦警方表示，他们调查出案件属恐怖行为，目的有可能是企图暗杀威尔克斯，但尚未清楚肇事者的明确动机<ref name=maja>{{cite web|url=http://www.dr.dk/Nyheder/Indland/2015/02/14/185325.htm|title=Politiet: Vi efterforsker skud på Østerbro som terror|first=Maja Lærke|last=Maach|work=dr.dk|date=14 February 2015|accessdate=14 February 2015|trans_title=Police: We investigate shots on Østerbro as terror|language=da|archive-date=2015-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150214190245/https://www.dr.dk/Nyheder/Indland/2015/02/14/185325.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wsj.com/articles/shots-fired-at-copenhagen-free-speech-event-1423932590|title=One Dead in Copenhagen Shooting That May Have Targeted Cartoonist|author=Sam Schechner|date=14 February 2015|work=WSJ|accessdate=14 February 2015|archive-date=2015-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150216004629/http://www.wsj.com/articles/shots-fired-at-copenhagen-free-speech-event-1423932590|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 犹太教堂枪击案 ==
[[File:Police_blockade_after_Copenhagen_shootings.jpg|thumb]]
次日凌晨00:50，哥本哈根市中心水晶街的犹太会堂再度爆发枪击案<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bt.dk/danmark/mosaisk-trossamfund-37-aarige-dan-blev-draebt-i-terrorangreb|title=Mosaisk Trossamfund: 37-årige Dan blev dræbt i terrorangreb|author=Søren Kjellberg Ishøy|date=15 February 2015|work=www.bt.dk|accessdate=15 February 2015|language=da|archive-date=2015-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150215124105/http://www.bt.dk/danmark/mosaisk-trossamfund-37-aarige-dan-blev-draebt-i-terrorangreb|dead-url=no}}</ref>。当时有80人在那里参加宗教仪式。

来自犹太社区38岁的丹·乌赞当时负责安保，后来因头部中枪身亡<ref name="auto">{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-31475803|title=Copenhagen hit by second deadly shooting|publisher=BBC News|date=15 February 2015|accessdate=15 February 2015|archive-date=2015-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150215120816/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-31475803|dead-url=no}}</ref>。枪手还朝两名丹麦安全和情报局官员的胳膊和腿部开枪<ref name="auto"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/02/15/us-denmark-shooting-synagogue-idUSKBN0LJ00H20150215|title=Shots fired at Copenhagen synagogue: Danish police|date=14 February 2015|publisher=Reuters|accessdate=2015-02-16|archive-date=2015-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150215234407/http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/02/15/us-denmark-shooting-synagogue-idUSKBN0LJ00H20150215|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=PET>{{cite web|url=http://www.staradvertiser.com/news/breaking/20150214_Police_1_dead_in_shooting_at_Copenhagen_free_speech_event.html?id=291957101|title=Denmark on edge as 2nd shooting within hours rocks capital|publisher=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]]|accessdate=14 February 2015|archive-date=2015-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150215053300/http://www.staradvertiser.com/news/breaking/20150214_Police_1_dead_in_shooting_at_Copenhagen_free_speech_event.html?id=291957101|dead-url=no}}</ref>。警方疏散了附近的Nørreport站，禁止列车停靠。此处是全国最繁忙的铁路枢纽，临近发生枪击案的犹太教堂<ref name="auto1">{{cite web|url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/2015-02-15/three-injured-in-copenhagen-synagogue-shooting/6107034|title=Copenhagen shootings: Police kill man close to scene of deadly synagogue and cafe attacks|work=ABC Online|date=15 February 2015|accessdate=15 February 2015}}</ref>。

== 反应 ==
通过[[闭路电视|监控摄像头]]录像，安全部队追踪到枪手<ref name="washingtonpost.com">{{cite web|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/danish-police-kill-copenhagen-shooting-suspect/2015/02/15/8bed7a70-b50a-11e4-9423-f3d0a1ec335c_story.html|title=Danish attacks echo France|work=Washington Post|accessdate=2015-04-12|archive-date=2015-05-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150508213857/http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/danish-police-kill-copenhagen-shooting-suspect/2015/02/15/8bed7a70-b50a-11e4-9423-f3d0a1ec335c_story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。警方2月15日04:50左右于哥本哈根北部Nørrebro车站附近的多种族社区开枪打死抢手<ref>{{cite web|url=http://politiken.dk/indland/ECE2547581/politiet-affyrer-skud-ved-noerrebro-station|title=Politiet har dræbt en mand ved Nørrebro Station|work=politiken.dk|date=15 February 2015|accessdate=15 February 2015|trans_title=Police kill man at Nørrebro Station|language=da|archive-date=2015-02-16|archive-url=https://archive.is/20150216085056/http://politiken.dk/indland/ECE2547581/politiet-affyrer-skud-ved-noerrebro-station|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="washingtonpost.com"/>。该名男子接近在警方监视下的一幢公寓楼，枪手在两起袭击间的空隙曾到过这里。警方叫了枪手一声，遭到枪手开火还击<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dr.dk/Nyheder/Indland/2015/02/15/055541.htm|title=Mand ramt af politiskud ved Nørrebro Station er død|publisher=Danmarks Radio|date=15 February 2015|accessdate=15 February 2015|trans_title=Man hit by police shots at Nørrebro Station dies|language=da|archive-date=2015-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150215092226/http://www.dr.dk/Nyheder/Indland/2015/02/15/055541.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。首席警督表示：“警方特种部队击毙的匪徒是潜藏在两起暗杀案背后的人物<ref name=dr073908>{{cite news|url=http://www.dr.dk/Nyheder/Indland/2015/02/15/073908.htm|title=Politi antager at have dræbt gerningsmanden|author=Peter Krogh Andersen|publisher=Danmarks Radio|date=15 February 2015|accessdate=15 February 2015|trans_title=Police believe they killed perpetrator|language=da|archive-date=2015-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150216014250/http://www.dr.dk/Nyheder/Indland/2015/02/15/073908.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="washingtonpost.com"/>。”

嫌疑枪手名叫奥马尔·阿卜杜勒·哈米德·侯赛因<ref name="auto2">{{cite news|last1=Green|first1=Chris|author2=Orange, Richard|title=Copenhagen shootings: Suspected gunman Omar Abdel Hamid El-Hussein was a Danish national with a history of gang violence|work=[[The_Independent|The Independent]]|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/copenhagen-shootings-suspected-gunman-omar-abdel-hamid-elhussein-was-a-danish-national-with-a-history-of-gang-violence-10047741.html|accessdate=16 February 2015|date=15 February 2015|archive-date=2015-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150925185934/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/copenhagen-shootings-suspected-gunman-omar-abdel-hamid-elhussein-was-a-danish-national-with-a-history-of-gang-violence-10047741.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="auto3">{{cite web|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/denmark/11413226/Copenhagen-shooting-during-debate-on-Islam.html|title=Copenhagen shooting during debate on Islam – Telegraph|date=15 February 2015|work=Telegraph.co.uk|accessdate=2015-02-16|archive-date=2015-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150216131220/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/denmark/11413226/Copenhagen-shooting-during-debate-on-Islam.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.co.uk/2015/02/15/omar-abdel-hamid-el-hussein_n_6688612.html|title=Copenhagen Shooting Suspect Omar Abdel Hamid El-Hussein Had Criminal Record, Police Say|work=The Huffington Post UK|accessdate=2015-02-16|archive-date=2015-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150216101321/http://www.huffingtonpost.co.uk/2015/02/15/omar-abdel-hamid-el-hussein_n_6688612.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thelocal.dk/20150215/suspected-gunman-born-and-raised-in-denmark|title=Suspected gunman born and raised in Denmark|work=thelocal.dk|accessdate=2015-02-16|archive-date=2015-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150421235443/http://www.thelocal.dk/20150215/suspected-gunman-born-and-raised-in-denmark|dead-url=no}}</ref>。丹麦警方表示该名22歲男子是丹麦情报部门的重点监视对象<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2015/02/shooting-targets-synagogue-denmark-capital-150215003951195.html|title=Police say Copenhagen attacks suspect killed|work=aljazeera.com|accessdate=2015-02-16|archive-date=2015-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150327161915/http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2015/02/shooting-targets-synagogue-denmark-capital-150215003951195.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="washingtonpost.com"/>。

2月16日，有两名男子被指控协助埃尔-侯赛因<ref>{{cite news|title=Men charged over Copenhagen attacks|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-31485086|accessdate=16 February 2015|work=BBC News|date=16 February 2015|archive-date=2015-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150216082003/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-31485086|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

55岁电影导演芬恩·诺佳德（Finn Nørgaard）在炸药桶咖啡馆袭击案中遇害<ref name="dr113410">{{cite web|url=http://www.dr.dk/Nyheder/Indland/2015/02/15/113410.htm|title=Filminstruktør var lørdagens første offer i København|author=Peter Krogh Andersen|publisher=Danmarks Radio|date=15 February 2015|accessdate=15 February 2015|trans_title=Film director was Saturday's first victim in Copenhagen|language=da|archive-date=2015-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150215124226/http://www.dr.dk/Nyheder/Indland/2015/02/15/113410.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，他曾导演和制作丹麦电视台的纪录片<ref name="auto3"/>。

38岁平民丹·乌赞在大教堂袭击案中被杀害<ref>{{cite web|work=Ynet news|url=http://www.ynet.co.il/articles/0,7340,L-4626623,00.html|title=Victim near the synagogue in Copenhagen: Dan Uzan, whose father was an Israeli|date=15 February 2015|accessdate=15 February 2015|language=he|archive-date=2015-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150215124204/http://www.ynet.co.il/articles/0,7340,L-4626623,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他住在犹太社区，有着以色列和丹麦血统，在约80人参与成年礼仪式时站在门口负责安保<ref name="jp">{{cite web|work=[[Jyllands-Posten|Jyllands-Posten]]|url=http://jyllands-posten.dk/indland/politiretsvaesen/ECE7451889/En-dr%C3%A6bt-i-skyderi-ved-K%C3%B8benhavns-synagoge|title=En dræbt i skyderi ved Københavns synagoge|date=15 February 2015|accessdate=15 February 2015|trans_title=One killed in Copenhagen Synagogue shooting|language=da|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150215124154/http://jyllands-posten.dk/indland/politiretsvaesen/ECE7451889/En-dr%C3%A6bt-i-skyderi-ved-K%C3%B8benhavns-synagoge/|archivedate=2015年2月15日}}</ref>。

