=== 国内 ===
丹麦女王[[玛格丽特二世_(丹麦)|玛格丽特二世]]透过[[Ritzau|Ritzau]]评论道：“我带着悲伤了解过去几天发生的事件。我认为遇害的导演和犹太社区年轻保安成了犯罪者的行动目标，”女王在一份书面评论中表示，“在这样一个严峻的形势下我们必须团结一致，珍惜丹麦所基于的价值观<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tv2oj.dk/artikel/244895:Kriminal--Dronningen-sender-sine-tanker-til-ofrene-for-terror|title=Dronningen sender sine tanker til ofrene for terror|publisher=TV 2/Østjylland|date=15 February 2015|accessdate=15 February 2015|quote=Mine tanker går til den dræbte filminstruktør og den unge vagtmand fra det jødiske samfund, som blev mål for gerningsmandens handlinger|trans_title=The Queen sends her thoughts to the victims of terror|language=da|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150215173824/http://www.tv2oj.dk/artikel/244895:Kriminal--Dronningen-sender-sine-tanker-til-ofrene-for-terror|archivedate=2015年2月15日}}</ref>。”首相[[赫勒·托宁-施密特|赫勒·托宁-施密特]]谴责“恐怖行为愤世嫉俗”，并表示，“我们还不知道袭击的动机，但我们坚信有股势力想要损害国家，希望粉碎我们的言论自由，我们的信仰自由。我们没有参与到伊斯兰国和西方国家之间的斗争中，这也不是一场穆斯林对抗非穆斯林的战斗<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.haaretz.com/news/world/1.642523 | title=Report: Suspected gunman behind Copenhagen attacks only just released from jail | work=Haaretz | date=15 February 2015 | accessdate=16 February 2015 | archive-date=2015-02-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150215181925/http://www.haaretz.com/news/world/1.642523 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.dpa-international.com/news/international/danish-security-copenhagen-shootings-inspired-by-paris-attacks-a-44254321-img-2.html | title=Copenhagen shootings likely "inspired" by Paris attacks | work=dpa Deutsche Presse-Agentur | date=15 February 2015 | accessdate=16 February 2015 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150216053317/http://www.dpa-international.com/news/international/danish-security-copenhagen-shootings-inspired-by-paris-attacks-a-44254321-img-2.html | archivedate=2015年2月16日 }}</ref>。”

教堂的拉比贾伊尔·梅尔基奥尔表示：“恐怖势力不是转移到以色列的原因……希望警方恪守职责（破案），但我们的生活自然还得继续。恐怖势力的目标是改变我们的生活，我们不能让它得逞……我们失去了亲爱的社区成员，现在我们应继承他的事业，继续像往常一样帮助生活在丹麦的犹太人。这才是对凶狠、残忍和懦弱的恐怖行为的回答<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/feb/15/european-jewish-association-protection-antisemitic-attacks-copenhagen|title=European Jewish Association calls for increased protection of institutions|author=Nadia Khomami|date=16 February 2015|work=The Guardian|accessdate=2015-02-16|archive-date=2015-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150216232458/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/feb/15/european-jewish-association-protection-antisemitic-attacks-copenhagen|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”[[丹麦伊斯兰议会|丹麦伊斯兰议会]]谴责了此次袭击，表示：“丹麦伊斯兰议会邀请每个丹麦社会人士在打击极端主义和恐怖主义的斗争中团结起来<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dr.dk/Nyheder/Indland/2015/02/15/0215003933.htm|title=Dansk Islamisk Råd: Håber gerningsmand fanges snart|publisher=Danmarks Radio|date=15 February 2015|accessdate=15 February 2015|trans_title=Danish Islamic Council: Hope the perpetrator will be caught soon|language=da|archive-date=2015-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150514021800/http://www.dr.dk/Nyheder/Indland/2015/02/15/0215003933.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://nyhederne.tv2.dk/krimi/2015-02-15-dansk-islamisk-raad-haaber-gerningsmand-fanges-snart|title=Dansk Islamisk Råd: Håber gerningsmand fanges snart|work=Nyhederne.tv2.dk|date=15 February 2015|accessdate=15 February 2015|trans_title=Danish Islamic Council: Hope the perpetrator will be caught soon|language=da|archive-date=2015-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151120153106/http://nyhederne.tv2.dk/krimi/2015-02-15-dansk-islamisk-raad-haaber-gerningsmand-fanges-snart|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”

