skyelig-voldsangrep-169001 |title= Solberg: – Et avskyelig voldsangrep |quote= Danmark rammet av et avskyelig voldsangrep. Vold og terror skal ikke begrense oss. Min omtanke til møtedeltakere, politi og det danske folk |date= 14 February 2015 |accessdate= 15 February 2015 |trans_title= Solberg: – an abominable attack of violence |language= no |archive-date= 2015-02-15 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150215054755/http://www.dagen.no/Nyheter/nyheter/Solberg-%E2%80%93-Et-avskyelig-voldsangrep-169001 |dead-url= no }}</ref>、[[罗马尼亚总统|罗马尼亚总统]][[克劳斯·约翰尼斯|克劳斯·约翰尼斯]]<ref>{{cite web |url= http://presidency.ro/?_RID=det&tb=date&id=15500&_PRID=lazi |title= Ref.: Președintele României, domnul Klaus Iohannis, condamnă cu fermitate atacurile teroriste de la Copenhaga |work= presidency.ro |date= 15 February 2015 |accessdate= 15 February 2015 |language= ro |archive-date= 2015-02-15 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150215211524/http://presidency.ro/?_RID=det&tb=date&id=15500&_PRID=lazi |dead-url= no }}</ref>和[[英国首相|英国首相]][[大卫·卡梅隆|大卫·卡梅隆]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/David_Cameron/status/566670568653869057|title=I condemn the shootings in #Copenhagen. #Freespeech must always be protected. My thoughts are with the Danish people.|date=14 February 2015|accessdate=2015-02-16|archive-date=2015-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150215124414/https://twitter.com/David_Cameron/status/566670568653869057|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[以色列总理|以色列总理]][[本雅明·内塔尼亚胡|本雅明·内塔尼亚胡]]表示“我们向丹麦人民和丹麦的犹太社区送去慰问。再次有犹太人仅仅因为是犹太人在欧洲的土地上遇害。这波恐怖袭击预计将持续，包括这些反犹太主义的凶残袭击。很显然犹太人应该受到每个国家的保护，但……以色列是每个犹太人的家……以色列张开双臂等待你的归来<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.timesofisrael.com/after-copenhagen-attack-pm-urges-that-jews-move-to-israel/|title=After Copenhagen attack, PM urges that Jews move to Israel|work=The Times of Israel|accessdate=15 February 2015|archive-date=2015-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150215162805/http://www.timesofisrael.com/after-copenhagen-attack-pm-urges-that-jews-move-to-israel/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”

=== 国际组织 ===
[[欧盟委员会|欧盟委员会]]发表声明谴责袭击：“欧盟委员会和驻哥本哈根高级代表谴责本次至少谋害两名公民生命并打伤数人的袭击。尽管生命是一个人最重要的事情，我们的思绪是跟受害者及其家人同在的。全欧洲与丹麦团结一致坚持言论自由和表达自由的权利。我们对抗反犹太主义和一切形式的歧视。欧洲不会被吓倒<ref>{{cite web|url=http://europa.eu/rapid/press-release_STATEMENT-15-4431_en.htm|title=Statement by the European Commission following today's shooting in Copenhagen.|date=14 February 2015|accessdate=2015-02-16|archive-date=2015-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150326193200/http://europa.eu/rapid/press-release_STATEMENT-15-4431_en.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”[[欧洲理事会|欧洲理事会]]主席[[唐纳德·图斯克|唐纳德·图斯克]]表示星期六的袭击“是针对我们的核心价值观和言论自由的另一种野蛮恐怖袭击<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/02/15/us-denmark-shooting-idUSKBN0LI0N720150215|title=Danish police say kill suspect in Copenhagen attacks|work=Reuters|accessdate=15 February 2015|archive-date=2015-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150216000925/http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/02/15/us-denmark-shooting-idUSKBN0LI0N720150215|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”

[[查禁目录|查禁目录]]首席执行官朱迪·金斯伯格表示，“自由表达、参与会议和辩论而不用担心暴力，是自由社会的基础，言论自由必须得到保护<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.indexoncensorship.org/2015/02/index-censorship-statement-blasphemy-debate-attack-copenhagen/|title=Index on Censorship statement on blasphemy debate attack in Copenhagen|date=14 February 2015|publisher=Index on Censorship|accessdate=2015-02-16|archive-date=2015-03-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150317032956/http://www.indexoncensorship.org/2015/02/index-censorship-statement-blasphemy-debate-attack-copenhagen/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”

[[伊扎布特|伊扎布特]]斯堪的纳维亚分部的新闻稿并未谴责袭击，但丹麦的政治家及其其他人都在责怪：“当你想到他们的手沾满多少鲜血，丹麦政客和舆论导向者都没有道德权威用暴力来指定穆斯林还是非穆斯林……我们身为一个穆斯林社群，应该不要在任何情况下屈服于压力或是接受前提，伊斯兰教正在被审判<ref>{{cite web|url=http://jyllands-posten.dk/indland/ECE7453442/Hizb-ut-Tahrir-Tag-ikke-afstand/|title=Hizb ut-Tahrir: Tag ikke afstand|work=jyllands-posten.dk|accessdate=2015-02-16|archive-date=2015-03-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150320092054/http://jyllands-posten.dk/indland/ECE7453442/Hizb-ut-Tahrir-Tag-ikke-afstand/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”

